modules.description: Provides functions to initiate QR code scanning, decode scanned data, and handle camera permissions. Works with string-based scan results and camera state indicators. Used to integrate real-time QR code reading into mobile applications for inventory tracking and user authentication.

The module provides control over QR scanner operations, including initiating scans, adjusting lighting, and managing camera previews, while querying error details and status flags. It works with error states, status values, and camera configurations to enable real-time adjustments and handling during scanning tasks.
